}} '''Threema'''是一款付费的开源[[端到端加密|端到端加密]][[即時通訊|即時通訊]]应用程式，可用於[[IOS|IOS]]和{{link-en|Android}}操作系統<ref>{{Cite web|title=Privacy gains traction with secure messaging apps|url=http://www.electronics-eetimes.com/en/privacy-gains-traction-with-secure-messaging-apps.html?cmp_id=7&news_id=222922448&vID=13&page=1|accessdate=21 December 2015|author=Happich|date=23 September 2014|first=Julien|work=Electronic Engineering Times Europe|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923235418/http://www.electronics-eetimes.com/en/privacy-gains-traction-with-secure-messaging-apps.html?cmp_id=7&news_id=222922448&vID=13&page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该軟體不需要电话号码或其他任何[[個人可識別資訊|个人身份資訊]]就能使用。这在一定程度上有助於用户匿名化<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cryptography Whitepaper|url=https://threema.ch/press-files/cryptography_whitepaper.pdf|accessdate=October 30, 2020|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921001417/https://threema.ch/press-files/cryptography_whitepaper.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=FAQ – Privacy Protection|url=https://threema.ch/en/faq/privacy_protection|accessdate=October 30, 2020|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609003234/https://threema.ch/en/faq/privacy_protection|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is a Threema ID?|url=https://threema.ch/en/faq/threema_id|work=threema.ch|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519002302/https://threema.ch/en/faq/threema_id|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

用戶可以通過該應用發送簡訊、进行语音和視訊通话，傳送[[多媒体|多媒体]]、位置、语音訊息和文件<ref name="What features does Threema offer">{{Cite web|title=What features does Threema offer?|url=https://threema.ch/en/faq/features|work=threema.ch|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609003120/https://threema.ch/en/faq/features|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用戶可以在電腦上使用Threema的[[網路应用程式|網路应用程式]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Threema Web|url=https://threema.ch/en/threema-web|accessdate=October 30, 2020|archive-date=2020-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315142318/https://threema.ch/en/threema-web|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但前提是用户必須在手機上安裝Threema且在线。

Threema是由瑞士公司Threema GmbH所开发<ref name="playstore">{{Cite web|title=Threema|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ch.threema.app|accessdate=5 July 2014|work=Google Play Store|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519002141/https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ch.threema.app|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="zefix">{{Cite web|title=Swiss company registry entry for Threema GmbH|url=http://sz.powernet.ch/webservices/inet/HRG/HRG.asmx/getHRGHTML?chnr=1304020462&amt=130&toBeModified=0&validOnly=0&lang=4&sort=0|accessdate=5 July 2014|author=Swiss Confederation|work=zefix.ch}}</ref>。產品[[伺服器|伺服器]]位于瑞士。截至2020年1月，Threema拥有800万用户<ref>{{Cite web|title=About - Threema: Best-Selling Chat App|url=https://threema.ch/en/about|language=en|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609003145/https://threema.ch/en/about|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2019年1月，有3000家公司和组织使用了商业版Threema Work<ref>{{Cite web|title=Verschlüsselte Botschaften|url=https://www.forbesdach.com/artikel/verschluesselte-botschaften.html|access-date=2021-04-12|archive-date=2019-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123022323/https://www.forbesdach.com/artikel/verschluesselte-botschaften.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

